SIBHEKA izindaba ezihamba phambili ezinkundleni zezindaba namhlanje. –  Ubuyela enkantolo uZandile Mafe osolwa ngokushisa iPhalamende –  Kulindeleke ukuthi inkantolo yoMthethosisekelo ikhiphe isinqumo sayo namuhla ngodaba lokumiswa kuka-Advocate Busisiwe Mkhwebane emsebenzini –  Isasezithebeni eyokushiswa kwamaloli kuleli, kulokhu kuzungeza ezinkundleni zokuxhumana ivideo ebonisa owesilisa ekhipha umshayeli weloli, kungena yena kulona anduba alithungele ngomlilo – URosemary Ndlovu nasolwa naye uNomusa Mudau basenkantolo ngecala lokuzama ukubulala umyeni kaMudau –  Kwezemidlalo, kwethulwa kwabezindaba iKZN Premier’s Cup enkundleni iMoses Mabhida Silandele kuzo zonke izinkundla zokuxhumana uthole izindaba ezihamba phambili @IsolezweNews